title: Blind Faith Goteborg Sweden 6.18.69
description:
Blind Faith - Konserthallen Liseberg, Liseberg Nojespark, Goteborg, Sweden, June 18th 1969, FM broadcast from FB master, best sounding version of this show i ever heard ! upgrade.

1. Well All Right 
2. I'd Rather See You Sleeping In The Ground 
3. Sea Of Joy 
4. Under My Thumb 
5. Can't Find My Way Home 
6. Do What You Like > Drum Solo > Do What You Like 
7. In The Presence Of The Lord  

Encores: 

8. Means To An End (1 light drop/glitch around minute 2:42)
9. Had To Cry Today 

Line Up :

Eric Clapton-Guitar & Vocals 
Steve Winwood-Keyboards & Vocals 
Ginger Baker-Drums 
Rick Grech-Bass & Violin 

Hello friends, just listen to the sound samples, in my little opinion, this is the best sounding 
version of this show i ever heard compare to all the others uploaded before here....this FM
audience recording sounds as a soundboard ! another one from my friend FB masters..

Taper : FB
Transfered, remastered & uploaded by 38f on Dime 2006.

Master cassette (nack) > behringer ultra curve pro deq 2496 audio equalizer > amplifiers > tascam audio cdrw750 > cd > computer > plex tool professional XL > wav > flac.
